title: Did you make a to-do list after Inslee’s stay home order was put in effect?
text: I’d love to see other Seattle Redditor’s to-do lists to help keep them focused and busy during these uncertain times! I’ve been keeping a weekly to-do list and it’s been nice to check things off during the week. I live in Seattle and after losing my job last month due to the coronavirus effecting the industry I worked in, I’ve felt a bit lost in the mix of staying at home and looking for work while keeping it together.
